body:
Features and Enhancements

Adequacy Enhancements
  • Updated Analysis Results page.
  • Added a Map to Analysis Results page
  • Updated Summary by Geography page
  • Modified csv exports
  • See the Adequacy tab on the Help page for more information.
Compare Networks - Strength Ratings
  • Do not include Strength Ratings when geography includes a population file that exceeds 2,000 total zips
    • Note: The population file may contain less than 2,000 zips but, when used with radius search, can increase to over 2,000.
    • If the population file exceeds the threshold, a message to the user will appear: "For speed of processing, strength star ratings are not available when the total number of selected and radius zips exceeds 2,000."

Issues Fixed

Performance Fine Tuning
  • Various fixes to improve performance when using large Population files.
